{"word":"H1431 - גָּדַל - gâdal - gaw-dal' - Advance","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">גָּדַל</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>gâdal"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>gaw-dal'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Advance"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பெரியவனாயிரு, வளர்ந்துபோ, தூக்கு, மேன்மைப்படு, வல்லமையாயிரு, பெரியதாயிரு, வளர், மகத்துவமாயிரு, மேன்மைப்படுத்து, மகிமைப்படுத்தப்படு, சீமானாயிரு, அருமையாயிரு, சிறந்தவனாயிரு, பெருமைப்பாராட்டு, வல்லவனாயிரு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to grow, to become great or important, to promote, to make powerful, to praise, to magnify, to do great things"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to grow up"},{"paragraph":"2) to become great"},{"paragraph":"3) to be magnified"},{"paragraph":"b) (Piel)"},{"paragraph":"1) to cause to grow"},{"paragraph":"2) to make great, to make powerful"},{"paragraph":"3) to magnify"},{"paragraph":"c) (Pual) to be brought up"},{"paragraph":"d) (Hiphil)"},{"paragraph":"1) to make great"},{"paragraph":"2) to magnify"},{"paragraph":"3) to do great things"},{"paragraph":"e) (Hithpael) to magnify oneself"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; properly to <i>twist</i> (compare <a href=\"#/H1434 - גְּדִל - gᵉdil - ghed-eel'/1434\">H1434</a>), that is, to <i>be</i> (causatively <i>make</i>) <i>large</i> (in various senses, as in body, mind, estate or honor, also in pride): - advance, boast, bring up, exceed, excellent, be (-come, do, give, make, wax), great (-er, come to . . estate, + things), grow (up), increase, lift up, magnify (-ifical), be much set by, nourish (up), pass, promote, proudly [spoken], tower."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1419 - גָּדֹול - gâdôwl - gaw-dole'/1419\">H1419</a>, <a href=\"#/H1420 - גְּדוּלָה - gᵉdûwlâh - ghed-oo-law'/1420\">H1420</a>, <a href=\"#/H1431 - גָּדַל - gâdal - gaw-dal'/1431\">H1431</a>, <a href=\"#/H1432 - גָּדֵל - gâdêl - gaw-dale'/1432\">H1432</a>, <a href=\"#/H1433 - גֹּדֶל - gôdel - go'-del/1433\">H1433</a>, <a href=\"#/H1434 - גְּדִל - gᵉdil - ghed-eel'/1434\">H1434</a>, <a href=\"#/H1435 - גִּדֵּל - Giddêl - ghid-dale'/1435\">H1435</a>, <a href=\"#/H1436 - גְּדַּלְיָה - Gᵉdalyâh - ghed-al-yaw'/1436\">H1436</a>, <a href=\"#/H1437 - גִּדַּלְתִּי - Giddaltîy - ghid-dal'-tee/1437\">H1437</a>, <a href=\"#/H3012 - יִגְדַּלְיָהוּ - Yigdalyâhûw - yig-dal-yaw'-hoo/3012\">H3012</a>, <a href=\"#/H4024 - מִגְדֹּול - Migdôwl - mig-dole'/4024\">H4024</a>, <a href=\"#/H4026 - מִגְדָּל - migdâl - mig-dawl'/4026\">H4026</a>, <a href=\"#/H4027 - מִגְדַּל־אֵל - Migdal-ʼÊl - mig-dal-ale'/4027\">H4027</a>, <a href=\"#/H4028 - מִגְדַּל־גָּד - Migdal-Gâd - migdal-gawd'/4028\">H4028</a>, <a href=\"#/H4029 - מִגְדַּל־עֵדֶר - Migdal-ʻÊder - mig-dal'-ay'-der/4029\">H4029</a>"}]}